column1: #Text=JavaScript Web Front End DeveloperSummary and Responsibilities...Build efficient, easy-to-use web experience to enable data exploration and data visualization on a large-scale knowledge graph, facilitate backend engineers to illustrate and debug service APIs.
#Text=Collaborate with back-end developers to design and implement E2E tooling, iterate based on feedbacks.
#Text=Perform troubleshooting for web application and debug application code.Qualifications 3+ years of experience working as a Front End developer, designing and implementing web applications.
#Text=Excellent hands-on knowledge of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript concepts, excellent front-end coding skills, and a good understanding of progressive web applications.
#Text=In-depth understanding of the entire web development process (design, development and deployment) Strong troubleshooting and problem-solving skills.
#Text=Strong interpersonal, verbal, and written communication skills.
